s vulnerability in `https://insider.razer.com` and I found this feature not at all working after enabled 2FA.\n\nPlease follow the below steps to reproduce the issue\n\n###Steps to reproduce\n1. Login to `https://insider.razer.com` with your credentials.\n2. Next, go to `Two-Step Verification` and set up your 2FA\n3. Now logout from the application and Login again\n4. You will observe it won't the ask the victim for the 2FA code it will simply log in to the dashboard\n5. I have tried login with different network and still, the issue can be reproduced.\n\n## Impact\n\n###Security Impact\nThe attacker always more curious about to bypass the victim's 2FA and by this vulnerability, if the victim's account got compromised then the attacker could able to easily bypass this security.\n\n###References\n1. https://shahmeeramir.com/4-methods-to-bypass-two-factor-authentication-2b0075d9eb5f\n2. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Y_NQbNQLg8\u0026t=556s\n\nThanks\nAnshuman Pattnaik","vulnerability_information_html":"\u003cp\u003eHello,\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI found 2FA bypass vulnerability in \u003ccode\u003ehttps://insider.razer.com\u003c/code\u003e and I found this feature not at all working after enabled 2FA.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003ePlease follow the below steps to reproduce the issue\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"steps-to-reproduce\"\u003eSteps to reproduce\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLogin to \u003ccode\u003ehttps://insider.razer.com\u003c/code\u003e with your credentials.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNext, go to \u003ccode\u003eTwo-Step Verification\u003c/code\u003e and set up your 2FA\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNow logout from the application and Login again\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou will observe it won\u0026#39;t the ask the victim for the 2FA code it will simply log in to the dashboard\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eI have tried login with different network and still, the issue can be reproduced.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003